Benjamin W. Stafford et al., plaintiffs in error, v. Herbert R. Phelps et al., defendants in error.Gen. No. 6,773.Bill praying for the construction of a will. Bill dismissed. Error to the Circuit Court of Will county; the Hon. Dorrance Dibell, Judge, presiding. Heard in this court at the October term, 1919.Affirmed.Opinion filed June 29, 1920.

Dibell, P. J., took no part.

George Warner Young, for plaintiffs in error. Frank G. Brumand, for defendants in error. Pence B. Orr, guardian ad litem for Dorothy Marshall. Mr. Justice Heard

delivered the opinion of the court.
